---
import Badge from './design-system/Badge.astro';
import Button from './design-system/Button.astro';
---

<section class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl items-center gap-10 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.15fr_0.85fr] lg:px-8 lg:py-20">
  <div>
    <div class="mb-4"><Badge>For students, families, and adult beginners</Badge></div>
    <h1 class="heading-display max-w-2xl">
      Learn Electronics by Building
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
      Engineering Maker Lab is a guided place to learn electronics through practical projects.
      Build circuits, understand how they work, and choose reusable gear with confidence.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
      <Button href="/start-here" class="w-full sm:w-auto">Start Here</Button>
      <Button href="/projects" variant="secondary" class="w-full sm:w-auto">Browse Projects</Button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-[var(--radius-card)] bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-700 to-sky-500 p-[1px] shadow-[var(--shadow-elevated)]">
    <div class="rounded-[calc(1.5rem-1px)] bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-5">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">Get equipped</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">1. Choose one kit</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Use one reusable set of parts across the learning path.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-5">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">Build progressively</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900">2. Finish five projects</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Move from a single LED to sensors, motion, and inputs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-5 sm:col-span-2">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">Keep learning</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-bold text-slate-900">3. Understand every circuit</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Focused tutorials explain the breadboard, GPIO, PWM, motors, and safe power.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
